      {
        summary: 'Localised Fat Treatment',
        title: 'SHOCK WAVES',
        body: `<p>Acoustic waves are extremely strong unfocused pulses that introduce vibrations into the body. The powerful energy of <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">BTL X-WAVE</strong> acoustic waves achieves the best results in non-invasive treatments of cellulite, scars and stretch marks.</p>
<h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zeniaRosaOscuro pt-2">CRYOLIPOLYSIS</h3>
<p>A non-invasive medical procedure for body fat elimination using <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">controlled intense cooling</strong>. Fat cells are the <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">most susceptible cells to cold</strong>. <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">Reduces 30%-40%</strong> of fat volume per session.</p>
<h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zeniaRosaOscuro pt-2">BODY CARBOXYTHERAPY</h3>
